{
  "id": "6a61fb606e1dea180124edca",
  "title": "「親父くさい」を通り越すほど古い趣味",
  "created": 1784806244,
  "updated": 1784808339,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a61fb606e1dea180124edca",
      "text": "「親父くさい」を通り越すほど古い趣味",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806244,
      "updated": 1784806244
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fb630000000000423457",
      "text": "[世代交代に失敗した仮死の文化]ともいう",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806244,
      "updated": 1784806930
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fb630000000000423458",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806244,
      "updated": 1784806244
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fb650000000000423459",
      "text": "今[親父くさい]とされるような趣味が全盛だった時代に「[親父くさい]」とされ、かつ[伝統になれなかったまま当時の世代が死に絶えた文化]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806245,
      "updated": 1784806322
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fb65000000000042345a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806245,
      "updated": 1784806245
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fd3a000000000042346e",
      "text": "つまり親父くさいを二回かけたほどに古い趣味",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806715,
      "updated": 1784806741
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fd3b000000000042346f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806715,
      "updated": 1784806715
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fc6a0000000000423466",
      "text": "[hoagecko.icon]は[のらくろ]の中古価格の定点観測をしていた時期があった",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806507,
      "updated": 1784806546
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fc920000000000423468",
      "text": "\t若干不謹慎だが[藤子不二雄A]の世代が亡くなったあたりでグンと価格帯が下がった",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806546,
      "updated": 1784806585
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fcb90000000000423469",
      "text": "\t\t二・三千円は変わった",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806585,
      "updated": 1784806593
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fcc3000000000042346a",
      "text": "\tファンが次世代へ引き継がれることなく死に絶えたると、文化的な影響力はなくなる",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806595,
      "updated": 1784806675
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fd13000000000042346c",
      "text": "\t\t「歴史的」と付く[仮死の文化]に変わる",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806675,
      "updated": 1784807091
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fd26000000000042346d",
      "text": "\t\t\t完全に死に絶えた百五十年以上前の文化とは違い、二～三十年ほど前に遺品として放出されまだ市場に出回っているなど、当時の生の情報がまだまだ簡単に手に入る違いがある",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806694,
      "updated": 1784806895
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fdb10000000000423470",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tつまりまだ死んだ世代から遺された記録のうちからその文化に「入門」できる",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806834,
      "updated": 1784806963
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fe340000000000423471",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\tそこが「[仮死の文化]」と表せる所以",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806964,
      "updated": 1784807094
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fc6a0000000000423467",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806507,
      "updated": 1784806507
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fb91000000000042345b",
      "text": "[hoagecko.icon]が取り合えず思いついた趣味を挙げてみる",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806289,
      "updated": 1784806864
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fc440000000000423464",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806468,
      "updated": 1784806474
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fbb5000000000042345f",
      "text": " 昭和初期の[SPレコード]の時代の文化と媒体",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806326,
      "updated": 1784807022
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fbcd0000000000423460",
      "text": " \t塩化ビニール以前のほぼ戦前の規格",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806350,
      "updated": 1784806372
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fc150000000000423462",
      "text": " \t一応若い世代のファンもいないわけではない",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806421,
      "updated": 1784806459
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fcd2000000000042346b",
      "text": "  初期のLPはまだ「親父くさい」で済んでいる印象",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806611,
      "updated": 1784807018
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fe500000000000423472",
      "text": " 大規模な[ダンスホール]での[ビッグバンド]をバックにした[社交ダンス]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784806993,
      "updated": 1784807082
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fe7c0000000000423474",
      "text": " \tこれは施設という環境由来だから違う気もする",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807037,
      "updated": 1784807115
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fe720000000000423473",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807026,
      "updated": 1784807352
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61ffb80000000000423476",
      "text": "[hoagecko.icon]が[chatgpt.icon]君に訊いて出してもらった回答で幾つかピックアップ",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807352,
      "updated": 1784807420
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fffb0000000000423477",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807420,
      "updated": 1784807420
    },
    {
      "id": "6a620057000000000042347f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807511,
      "updated": 1784807511
    },
    {
      "id": "6a6200570000000000423480",
      "text": "音楽",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807511,
      "updated": 1784807513
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fffb0000000000423478",
      "text": " [のど自慢]巡業追っかけ",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807420,
      "updated": 1784807426
    },
    {
      "id": "6a6200030000000000423479",
      "text": " \t昔は居たらしいが最近は確かに聞かない[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807428,
      "updated": 1784807729
    },
    {
      "id": "6a61fecb0000000000423475",
      "text": " [マンドリン]合奏団（社会人）",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807116,
      "updated": 1784807518
    },
    {
      "id": "6a620031000000000042347b",
      "text": " \t学生サークルはまだあるらしいが…",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807474,
      "updated": 1784807485
    },
    {
      "id": "6a62000c000000000042347a",
      "text": " ハワイアン・バンドブーム",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807436,
      "updated": 1784807509
    },
    {
      "id": "6a620050000000000042347e",
      "text": "  スチールギター演奏",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807504,
      "updated": 1784807509
    },
    {
      "id": "6a6201f800000000004234a0",
      "text": " ビッグバンド付きの社交ダンス",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807928,
      "updated": 1784807933
    },
    {
      "id": "6a6201fe00000000004234a1",
      "text": "  [hoagecko.icon]が既に挙げた",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807935,
      "updated": 1784807939
    },
    {
      "id": "6a620040000000000042347c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807489,
      "updated": 1784807489
    },
    {
      "id": "6a6200b70000000000423481",
      "text": "メディア別娯楽",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807608,
      "updated": 1784807665
    },
    {
      "id": "6a6200bc0000000000423484",
      "text": " [ラジオドラマ]同好会",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807612,
      "updated": 1784807620
    },
    {
      "id": "6a6200c50000000000423485",
      "text": " \tASMR系の「[ボイスドラマ]」に引き継がれたか？[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807621,
      "updated": 1784807643
    },
    {
      "id": "6a6200f30000000000423487",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807668,
      "updated": 1784807668
    },
    {
      "id": "6a6200f40000000000423488",
      "text": "メディアそのもの",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807668,
      "updated": 1784807672
    },
    {
      "id": "6a6200f7000000000042348b",
      "text": " [オープンリール]録音会",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807672,
      "updated": 1784807755
    },
    {
      "id": "6a62013d0000000000423494",
      "text": " [活字組版]研究",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807741,
      "updated": 1784807745
    },
    {
      "id": "6a6201d4000000000042349f",
      "text": " [テレタイプ通信]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807893,
      "updated": 1784807896
    },
    {
      "id": "6a62010b000000000042348c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807692,
      "updated": 1784807692
    },
    {
      "id": "6a62010c000000000042348d",
      "text": "コレクション",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807692,
      "updated": 1784807693
    },
    {
      "id": "6a62010d000000000042348e",
      "text": " マッチラベル収集",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807693,
      "updated": 1784807695
    },
    {
      "id": "6a62010d000000000042348f",
      "text": " テレホンカード収集",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807693,
      "updated": 1784807697
    },
    {
      "id": "6a62010d0000000000423492",
      "text": " 煙草ラベル収集",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807693,
      "updated": 1784807698
    },
    {
      "id": "6a62010d0000000000423493",
      "text": " 王冠（瓶の王冠）収集",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807693,
      "updated": 1784807698
    },
    {
      "id": "6a6200f60000000000423489",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807670,
      "updated": 1784807670
    },
    {
      "id": "6a620196000000000042349c",
      "text": "他生活関係",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807831,
      "updated": 1784807835
    },
    {
      "id": "6a6201650000000000423495",
      "text": " 街頭テレビ文化",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807781,
      "updated": 1784807830
    },
    {
      "id": "6a62019e000000000042349e",
      "text": "  現状、電気屋で鑑賞目的でテレビを覗くのはヒマしてる子供ぐらいだ[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807838,
      "updated": 1784807912
    },
    {
      "id": "6a62018d0000000000423499",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807822,
      "updated": 1784808334
    },
    {
      "id": "6a62019b000000000042349d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "688c296691686a314f82fb52",
      "created": 1784807836,
      "updated": 1784807836
    }
  ]
}